.Dd June 10, 2026
.Dt LIBCTHREADS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm libcthreads.h
.Nd Library to support cross-platform C threads functions
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In libcthreads.h
.Pp
Support functions
.nf
.Ft const char *
.Fo libcthreads_get_version
.Fa "void"
.Fc
.fi
.Pp
